Package: functionR
Type: Package
Title: Utility functions for embedding ggplot previews in HTML
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Anbunensi", family = "", email = "anbunengsi@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Small collection of helper functions to render ggplot objects into embedded PNG data URIs and produce an HTML dropdown preview (for use in Quarto / R Markdown). The package is lightweight and focused on report embedding workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
